OL,3,CSpecial forces boss covered up
OL,4,Cpotential war crimes in Afghanistan,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,FThe head of the UK's special forces
OL,8,Fcovered up potential war crimes in
OL,9,FAfghanistan and used tactical reviews
OL,10,Fto sweep rumours under the rug, an
OL,11,Finquiry has been told.
OL,13,FThe Afghanistan Inquiry has released
OL,14,Fsummaries of closed hearings in which
OL,15,Fmembers of special forces (UKSF) have
OL,16,Fgiven evidence about alleged murders
OL,17,Fbetween 2010 and 2013.
