OL,7,FA senior officer, known only to the
OL,8,Fprobe as N1466, said he believed
OL,9,Fstatistics from deliberate detention
OL,10,Foperations, including the number of
OL,11,Fweapons found compared to enemies
OL,12,Fkilled in action, "didn't seem
OL,13,Fcredible", a view he believed was
OL,14,Fshared by the director of UK special
OL,15,Fforces (DSF).
