OL,7,FIn his witness statement, N1466 said:
OL,8,F"I felt at the time that N1802
OL,9,Fintended that the TTP review would
OL,10,Fhave the effect of firing a warning
OL,11,Fshot across the bows of the sub-unit
OL,12,Fto encourage them to change their
OL,13,Fbehaviour.
OL,15,F"I was sure at the time, and I remain
OL,16,Fsure that N1802 knew what was
OL,17,Fhappening on the ground.
