OL,3,CSpecial forces boss covered up
OL,4,Cpotential war crimes in Afghanistan,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,FIn a note dated April 7, 2011, N1466
OL,8,Ftold the DSF a commanding officer of a
OL,9,Fspecial forces unit had informed him
OL,10,Fof a "deliberate policy" among some
OL,11,Fmembers to "kill fighting-aged males
OL,12,F... even when they did not pose a
OL,13,Fthreat".
OL,15,FN1466 claims he has decided to speak
OL,16,Fout because "I believe that our
OL,17,Fforebears will look back on that with
OL,18,Fshame."
