OL,7,FHe added: "The activity that we have
OL,8,Fdiscussed in the last few days does
OL,9,Fnot fit with that and somehow the
OL,10,Famount of kills and the amount of
OL,11,Ftrigger time have become the metric by
OL,12,Fwhich people judge themselves."
OL,14,FAfghan families have accused UKSF of
OL,15,Fconducting a "campaign of murder"
OL,16,Fagainst civilians, while claiming
OL,17,Fsenior officers and personnel at the
OL,18,FMinistry of Defence "sought to prevent
OL,19,Fadequate investigation".
