OL,4,Cpotential war crimes in Afghanistan,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,FN1466 told the inquiry about an
OL,8,Fincident in which an Afghan man burst
OL,9,Finto a meeting between a UKSF sub-unit
OL,10,Fand their Afghan partner unit before
OL,11,Fpointing a pistol at a senior UKSF
OL,12,Fofficer and saying, "these guys are
OL,13,Fall murdering our people".
OL,15,FConcluding his evidence, N1466 said
OL,16,Fthe alleged murders by members of UKSF
OL,17,Fin Afghanistan did not help
OL,18,Fconventional forces, adding that it
OL,19,Fwas "a stain against their sacrifice
OL,20,Fand their service".
