OL,8,Fwritten to special forces personnel,
OL,9,Frecognising their professionalism and
OL,10,Fsacrifice and telling them the
OL,11,Fgovernment "has your back", it is
OL,12,Funderstood.
OL,14,FA Ministry of Defence spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid: "The government is fully
OL,16,Fcommitted to supporting the
OL,17,Findependent inquiry relating to
OL,18,FAfghanistan as it continues its work,
OL,19,Fand we are hugely grateful to all
OL,20,Fformer and current defence employees
OL,21,Fwho have so far given evidence.
